# [(${chat.name})]

* **User:** [(${chat.user})]
* **Start:** [(${#dates.format(chat.createdAt, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')})]
* **End / Last Change:** [(${#dates.format(chat.modifiedAt, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')})]

---
[# th:each="turn : ${chat.turns}"]
_**Request:**_
[# th:if="${turn.chatModeChanged}"]
* **Mode:** [(${turn.chatMode})]
[/][# th:each="line : ${escapedMarkdownLines.apply(turn.request)}"]
> [(${line})]
[/]
_**Response:**_
[# th:if="${turn.modelChanged}"]
* **Model:** [(${turn.modelName})]
[/][# th:if="${turn.referencesChanged && !turn.references.isEmpty()}"]
* **References:** [# th:each="reference : ${turn.references}"]
  * [ [(${reference.name})] ]([(${reference.uri})])
[/][/][# th:if="${!turn.steps.isEmpty()}"]
* **Steps:** [# th:each="step : ${turn.steps}"]
  * [(${stepStatusToSymbol.apply(step.status)})] [(${step.title})][# th:if="${step.errorMessage != null}"]<br /><span style="color: red">[(${step.errorMessage})]</span>[/]
[/][/][# th:if="${!turn.thinking.isEmpty()}"]
* **Thinking:** [# th:each="t : ${turn.thinking}"]
  * 🧠 **[(${t.title})]**[# th:if="${!t.content.isEmpty()}"]
    [# th:each="line : ${rawBlockquoteLines.apply(t.content)}"]
    > [(${line})]
    [/][/]
[/][/][# th:if="${!turn.workingSet.isEmpty()}"]
* **Edited files:** [# th:each="f : ${turn.workingSet}"]
  * 📝 [(${workingSetEntry.apply(f)})]
[/][/][# th:if="${turn.errorMessage != null}"]
* **⚠️ Error:** [(${turn.errorMessage})]
[/][# th:if="${turn.rating != null}"]
* **Rating:** [# th:if="${turn.rating > 0}"]👍[/][# th:if="${turn.rating < 0}"]👎[/][# th:if="${turn.rating == 0}"]±0[/]
[/]
[(${turn.response})]

---

[/]_**End of Chat**_